      "title": "EduAakashaa — Psychometric Career Stream Assessment",
      "bodyText": "eduaakashaa.in\nEA\nPsychometric Career Assessment\nBY EDUAAKASHAA\nA comprehensive, scientifically-designed assessment with 60+ questions across psychometric profiling, aptitude testing, practical application, and subject confidence — delivering personalized stream recommendations with visual analytics, career roadmaps, and action plans.\n🧠\nPsychometric\n15 Qs · Personality\n📐\nAptitude\n15 Qs · Logic & Math\n🎯\nApplication\n15 Qs · Real Scenarios\n📊\nSubject Confidence\nReadiness Check\n🏆\nTop 10 Careers\nCourses + AI Impact\n📋\nAction Plan\nVisual Report + PDF\nBegin Assessment →\n\n~25-30 min · Saved to Google Sheets · PDF to Google Drive",
